---
import SectionHeading from '../ui/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section id="problem-section" class="section section-dark problem-section-custom">
  <div class="container">
    <SectionHeading 
      eyebrow="The Pain Points"
      title="Sound Familiar?"
      subtitle="Running a business is hard enough without the stress of manual bookkeeping."
    />

    <div class="grid grid-3 problem-grid">
      <!-- Pain 1 -->
      <div class="custom-problem-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="problem-icon-wrapper">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><line x1="10" y1="9" x2="8" y2="9"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="problem-card-title">Drowning in Receipts & Spreadsheets</h3>
        <p class="problem-card-desc">Spending late nights reconciling transactions, chasing missing invoices, and manual data entry. Every hour on your books is an hour lost on growing your revenue.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain 2 -->
      <div class="custom-problem-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="problem-icon-wrapper">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="problem-card-title">Dreading Tax Season Every Year</h3>
        <p class="problem-card-desc">The annual scramble to organize receipts, figure out tax write-offs, and compile spreadsheets. Fearing late-filing IRS penalties or paying more than you actually owe.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain 3 -->
      <div class="custom-problem-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="problem-icon-wrapper">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"></line><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"></line><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="problem-card-title">Flying Blind on Cash Flow</h3>
        <p class="problem-card-desc">Making business decisions without knowing your exact margins or profits. Without real-time visibility, you might overcommit, miss payroll, or lose growth opportunities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-footer text-center reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="transition-badge">
        <span class="transition-text">It doesn't have to be this way.</span>
        <a href="#services-grid-section" class="transition-link">
          Explore our solutions 
          <svg class="chevron-right" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-section-custom {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-primary-dark) 0%, #030f26 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Ambient background glow */
  .problem-section-custom::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -20%;
    width: 80%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.03) 0%, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0) 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .problem-grid {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
  }

  .custom-problem-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transition: transform var(--transition-normal), box-shadow var(--transition-normal), border-color var(--transition-normal), background-color var(--transition-normal);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .custom-problem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.25);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -15px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
  }

  .problem-icon-wrapper {
    color: #FF5252; /* Vibrant warning red */
    background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.12);
    padding: var(--space-3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .custom-problem-card:hover .problem-icon-wrapper {
    transform: scale(1.08) rotate(-3deg);
  }

  .problem-card-title {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-white);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .problem-card-desc {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-sm);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .problem-footer {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
  }

  .transition-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .transition-badge {
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: var(--space-4);
      padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-6);
    }
  }

  .transition-text {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .transition-link {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-secondary-light);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-1);
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .transition-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .chevron-right {
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .transition-link:hover .chevron-right {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>
